This code uses a while loop to find the moves, and it iterates from `k-1` to `1` to find the largest jump that doesn't make the position divisible by `k`. It then appends the remaining position to the moves list. The code also handles the case when the position is divisible by `k` by subtracting 1 from the position and appending 1 to the moves list.

